Cloning the Project from the github in gitbash

1)  git clone https://github.com/Gowtham4065/Dynamic-Form.git

In command prompt, go to the following cloned project

2) npm install   ---> Execute this command to install all the node modules

3) npm start -----> will run the application in http://localhost:3000/

4) npm run build -> to build the application

5) npm install -g firebase-tools -> To install the firebase tools

6) firebase login -> To login into the firebase

7) firebase init -> Intialize your project

8) firebase deploy -> To deploy the project

The following link has the hosted application

https://dynamicform-466f4.web.app/


